sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant API as moling-api
    participant GenSvc as GenerationService
    participant AlgoSvc as AlgorithmService
    participant VaultFlt as VaultFilterService
    participant Conflict as ConflictDetectionService
    participant DirScore as DirectionScoringService
    participant WeaveSch as WeavingSchemeService
    participant PromptSvc as PromptService
    participant LLM as DeepSeekClient
    participant Coherence as CoherenceService
    participant SecretSvc as SecretService
    participant MergeSvc as MergeService
    participant Phase4 as Phase4Service
    participant CardSvc as CardService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Redis

    User->>API: POST /generation/start
    API->>GenSvc: start_generation(project_id, chapter_id, req)
    GenSvc->>DB: 验证项目归属 + 章节存在
    GenSvc->>DB: 创建 GenerationTask (status=pending)
    GenSvc-->>API: { task_id, status }
    API-->>User: 202 Accepted

    Note over GenSvc: Worker 异步执行 12-Step Pipeline

    GenSvc->>DB: 更新 status=running, progress=10%

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over GenSvc,AlgoSvc: Step 1-6: 算法编排
        GenSvc->>AlgoSvc: step1_weight_allocation(cards, user_weights)
        AlgoSvc-->>GenSvc: weight_map

        GenSvc->>VaultFlt: step2_vault_filter(cards)
        VaultFlt->>DB: 查询四库数据（角色/时间线/伏笔/世界观）
        VaultFlt-->>GenSvc: filtered_vault (含压缩层级)

        GenSvc->>Conflict: step3_conflict_detection(cards, weight_map)
        Conflict->>DB: 获取动态层 + 秘密矩阵
        Conflict-->>GenSvc: conflict_results (含U曲线置信度)

        GenSvc->>DirScore: step4_direction_scoring(cards, weight_map)
        DirScore-->>GenSvc: direction_scores (含相容性评分)

        GenSvc->>WeaveSch: step5_match_weaving_scheme(cards, weight_map)
        WeaveSch-->>GenSvc: weaving_scheme (模式+大纲+指令)

        GenSvc->>AlgoSvc: step6_fill_outline(scheme, context)
        AlgoSvc-->>GenSvc: filled_outline
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over GenSvc,LLM: Step 7-8: Prompt组装 + LLM调用
        GenSvc->>PromptSvc: build_full_prompt(Layer 0-4 context)
        PromptSvc-->>GenSvc: final_prompt

        GenSvc->>LLM: chat(messages, model, temperature, max_tokens)
        LLM-->>GenSvc: generated_content
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over GenSvc,MergeSvc: Step 9-12: 后处理
        GenSvc->>SecretSvc: extract_secrets_from_content(content)
        SecretSvc->>LLM: 秘密提取 prompt
        SecretSvc->>DB: 保存提取的秘密
        SecretSvc-->>GenSvc: extracted_secrets

        GenSvc->>Coherence: validate_post_generation(content)
        Coherence->>DB: 获取四库 + 动态层上下文
        Coherence->>LLM: 3组分组一致性检查
        Coherence-->>GenSvc: validation_result

        GenSvc->>MergeSvc: auto_merge(HIGH/MEDIUM confidence)
        MergeSvc->>DB: 四库合并写入
        MergeSvc-->>GenSvc: merge_results

        GenSvc->>DB: 更新动态层状态
        GenSvc->>CardSvc: refresh_card_pool(chapter_id)
        CardSvc->>DB: 从四库变更生成新卡牌
    end

    GenSvc->>DB: 更新 status=completed, progress=100%

    Note over Phase4: 用户确认章节后触发 Phase4 收纳

    User->>API: POST /phase4/confirm
    API->>Phase4: confirm_storage(project_id, chapter_id, nonce)
    Phase4->>Redis: 检查 nonce (幂等)
    Phase4->>DB: 创建 Phase4Task (status=queued)
    Phase4-->>API: { task_id, status }
    API-->>User: 202 Accepted

    Phase4->>LLM: 四库变更提取 (EXTRACTION_SCHEMA)
    LLM-->>Phase4: extraction_result
    Phase4->>Phase4: SourceText Grounding (编辑距离验证)
    Phase4->>MergeSvc: apply_merges(extraction_result)
    MergeSvc->>DB: 角色/时间线/伏笔/世界观四库写入
    Phase4->>DB: 更新动态层
    Phase4->>CardSvc: refresh_card_pool()
    Phase4->>CardSvc: check_and_retire()
    Phase4->>Redis: 标记 nonce 已处理
